  "prompt": "What is best free one page theme for WordPress?",
  "response": "There are several excellent free one-page themes for WordPress that you can consider. Here are some of the popular and well-rated options:\n\n1. **Zerif Lite**: This is a responsive one-page theme that is great for business websites. It has a clean and modern design, is easy to customize, and supports various plugins.\n\n2. **Hestia**: Hestia offers a stylish, modern look with a one-page layout. It is compatible with WooCommerce, making it a good option for eCommerce sites, and it is also responsive and SEO-friendly.\n\n3. **OnePress**: This is a simple and elegant one-page theme suitable for businesses and freelancers. It is fully responsive and comes with a customizable homepage.\n\n4. **Sydney**: Sydney is a powerful business theme that also offers a one-page layout. It has a modern design, various customization options, and is compatible with page builders for more flexibility.\n\n5. **Allegiant**: This theme provides a professional look with a flexible layout, ideal for businesses, agencies, and portfolios. It integrates well with popular plugins and includes a one-page option.\n\n6. **OceanWP**: While not exclusively a one-page theme, OceanWP is highly versatile and can be configured to create a one-page website. It is responsive and offers many customization options.\n\n7. **Shapely**: Shapely is a feature-rich one-page theme that integrates with various plugins, making it suitable for portfolios, landing pages, and business sites.\n\n8. **Ascend**: This is a flexible and multipurpose theme that offers a one-page design. It has various customization options and is built with a focus on performance.\n\nWhen selecting a theme, consider your specific needs, such as the type of website you\u2019re building, your design preferences, and required features. Always check the theme ratings and support options as well.",
